		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.304</ph> Small disadvantaged business status.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d1146e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1160e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer may accept an offerorâ€™s representation that it is a small disadvantaged business concern (SDB) concern.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1160e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The provision at <xref href="FAR-i1057235.dita#i1057235"
                        base="i1057235"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-1</xref>, Small Business Program Representations, or <xref href="FAR-i1060550.dita#i1060550"
                        base="i1060550"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.212-3</xref>(c)(4), Offeror Representations and Certifications-Commercial Items, is used to collect SDB data.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1160e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A representation of SDB status on a Federal prime contract will be deemed a misrepresentation of SDB status if the firm does not meet the requirements of 13 CFR 124.1001(b).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1160e50" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Any person or entity that misrepresents a firm's status as an SDB concern in order to obtain a contracting opportunity in accordance with section 8(d) of the Small Business Act, (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref "> 15 U.S.C. 637(d)</xref>) will be subject to the penalties imposed by section 16(d) of the Small Business Act, (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref "> 15 U.S.C. 645(d)</xref>), as well as any other penalty authorized by law.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
